  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK157">
<l>tiṟaṉalla taṟpiṟar ceyyiṉu nōnon</l>
<l>taṟaṉalla ceyyāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though others inflict injuries on you, yet compassionating the evil (that will come upon them) it will be well not to do them anything contrary to virtue.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
